Table_Level_2_Measures_2.query:
MasterHierarchy = load "Master_Hierarchy";
MasterHierarchy = filter MasterHierarchy by 'Level_1' in   {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};

---------------------LOAD/FILTER ACV---------------------
ACV = load "APM_ACV";
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(lens_2.selection,["Region"]).asEquality('Region')}};
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(Filter_Lead_1.selection,["Lead_1"]).asEquality('Lead_1')}};
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(Filter_Segment.selection,["Segment"]).asEquality('Segment')}};
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(Filter_Industry.selection,["Industry"]).asEquality('Industry')}};
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(Filter_Lead.selection,["Lead"]).asEquality('Lead')}};
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(Filter_Cloud.selection,["Cloud"]).asEquality('Cloud')}};
ACV = filter ACV by 'Cloud' in  {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
ACV = group ACV by ('Cloud','Cloud_2','Subcloud', 'Quarter','Month', 'Fiscal_Year', 'Region' , 'Country');

ACV = foreach ACV generate  'Cloud' as 'Cloud', 'Subcloud' as 'Subcloud','Cloud_2' as 'Cloud_2', 'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year' ,'Month' as 'Month',sum('ACV') as 'ACV', 'Region' as 'Region',  {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country' ; ACV = filter ACV by  {{column(lens_1.selection,["Country"]).asEquality('Country')}};

q2_CYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}} ;

-----------------LOAD /FILTER HC-----------------------
HC = load "APM_HC";
HC = filter HC by {{column(lens_2.selection,["Region"]).asEquality('Region')}};
HC = foreach HC generate  'Cloud' as 'Cloud', 'Subcloud' as 'Subcloud','Cloud_2' as 'Cloud_2', 'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year','Month' as 'Month' ,sum('SE') as 'SE', sum('AE') as 'AE', sum('Co_Prime') as 'Co_Prime','Region' as 'Region', {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country' ; HC = filter HC by  {{column(lens_1.selection,["Country"]).asEquality('Country')}};
HC = filter HC by 'Cloud' in  {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
q2_CYHC = filter HC by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q2_PYHC = filter HC by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q2_PY_2_HC = filter HC by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY_2").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_CYHC = filter HC by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter_HC").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_PYHC = filter HC by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter_HC").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_PY_2_HC = filter HC by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter_HC").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY_2").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});

----------------------AE PARTICIPATION-----------------------------
PARTICIPATION = load "APM_AE";
PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by {{column(lens_2.selection,["Region"]).asEquality('Region')}};
PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by 'Region' == "N/A";
PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by 'Lead' == "N/A";
PARTICIPATION = foreach PARTICIPATION generate 'Cloud' as 'Cloud', 'Subcloud' as 'Subcloud','Cloud_2' as 'Cloud_2', 'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year','Month' as 'Month' ,sum('Cloud_m1') as 'Cloud_m1', sum('Cloud_m2') as 'Cloud_m2', sum('Cloud_m3') as 'Cloud_m3', 'Region' as 'Region',  {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country'; 
PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by  {{column(lens_1.selection,["Country"]).asEquality('Country')}};
PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' in {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};

q2_CYPARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYPARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PY_2_PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY_2").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYPARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter").asString()}}) && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYPARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter").asString()}}) && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PY_2_PARTICIPATION = filter PARTICIPATION by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter").asString()}}) && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY_2").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};

------------------------GROUPING LEVEL_1 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
result = group 
q2_CYACV by 'Cloud' full, 
q2_PYACV by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_CYACV by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_PYACV by 'Cloud' full, 

q2_CYHC by 'Cloud' full, 
q2_PYHC by 'Cloud' full,
q2_PY_2_HC by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_CYHC by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_PYHC by 'Cloud' full,
q3_PY_2_HC by 'Cloud' full,

q2_CYPARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' full, 
q2_PYPARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' full, 
q2_PY_2_PARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_CYPARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_PYPARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' full, 
q3_PY_2_PARTICIPATION by 'Cloud' full, 

MasterHierarchy by 'Level_1';

-------------------PROJECTION CLOUD-----------------------------------
result = foreach result generate 
" " + coalesce(MasterHierarchy.'Level_1', q2_CYACV.'Cloud', q2_PYACV.'Cloud', q3_CYACV.'Cloud', q3_PYACV.'Cloud') as 'Cloud',  

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute', coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Absolute', ((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth', ((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD ACV Growth',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'SE'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} SE Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'SE'), 0) as 'YTD SE Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'SE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} SE Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'SE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD SE Growth',
(power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'SE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_HC.'SE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} SE CAGR',
(power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'SE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_HC.'SE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as 'YTD SE CAGR', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'AE'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} AE Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'AE'), 0) as 'YTD AE Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'AE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} AE Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'AE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD AE Growth', 
(power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'AE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_HC.'AE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} AE CAGR',
(power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'AE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_HC.'AE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as 'YTD AE CAGR',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Co_Prime Absolute', coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) as 'YTD Co_Prime Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Co_Prime Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Co_Prime Growth',
(power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_HC.'Co_Prime'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Co_Prime CAGR',
(power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_HC.'Co_Prime'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as 'YTD Co_Prime CAGR',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Participation Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0) as 'YTD Participation Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Participation Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m1'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Participation Growth'

;

-------------------------------GROUPING LEVEL_2-------------------
result_SubCloud = group 
q2_CYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q2_PYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_CYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_PYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 

q2_CYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q2_PYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full,
q2_PY_2_HC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_CYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_PYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_PY_2_HC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full ,

q2_CYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q2_PYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q2_PY_2_PARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_CYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_PYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 
q3_PY_2_PARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud') full, 

MasterHierarchy by ('Level_1', 'Level_2') ;

--------------------------------PROJECTION LEVEL_2------------------------------------
result_SubCloud = foreach result_SubCloud generate 
"  " + coalesce(MasterHierarchy.'Level_2', q2_CYACV.'Subcloud', q2_PYACV.'Subcloud', q3_CYACV.'Subcloud', q3_PYACV.'Subcloud') as 'Cloud',  

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute', coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Absolute', ((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth', ((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD ACV Growth', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'SE'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} SE Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'SE'), 0) as 'YTD SE Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'SE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} SE Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'SE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'SE'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD SE Growth',
(power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'SE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_HC.'SE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} SE CAGR',
(power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'SE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_HC.'SE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as 'YTD SE CAGR', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'AE'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} AE Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'AE'), 0) as 'YTD AE Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'AE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} AE Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'AE'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'AE'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD AE Growth', 
(power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'AE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_HC.'AE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} AE CAGR',
(power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'AE'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_HC.'AE'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as 'YTD AE CAGR',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Co_Prime Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) as 'YTD Co_Prime Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Co_Prime Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Co_Prime Growth',
(power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_HC.'Co_Prime'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Co_Prime CAGR',
(power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYHC.'Co_Prime'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_HC.'Co_Prime'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100 as 'YTD Co_Prime CAGR', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Participation Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0) as 'YTD Participation Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Participation Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYPARTICIPATION.'Cloud_m2'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Participation Growth',

last(MasterHierarchy.'Level_2_Sort_Code')  as 'Sort_Code';
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------GROUPING LEVEL3-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
result_Cloud_Level3 = group  
q2_CYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud', 'Cloud_2') full, 
q2_PYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud', 'Cloud_2') full, 
q3_CYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud', 'Cloud_2') full, 
q3_PYACV by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud', 'Cloud_2') full, 

q2_CYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q2_PYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full,
q2_PY_2_HC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q3_CYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q3_PYHC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full,  
q3_PY_2_HC by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full,

q2_CYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q2_PYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q2_PY_2_PARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q3_CYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q3_PYPARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full, 
q3_PY_2_PARTICIPATION by ('Cloud', 'Subcloud','Cloud_2') full,  

MasterHierarchy by ('Level_1', 'Level_2','Level_3')  ;
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------PROJECTION LEVEL3-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

result_Cloud_Level3 = foreach result_Cloud_Level3 generate 
"" + coalesce(MasterHierarchy.'Level_3', q2_CYACV.'Cloud_2', q2_PYACV.'Cloud_2', q3_CYACV.'Cloud_2', q3_PYACV.'Cloud_2') as 'Cloud',

lens_1.label: Country logic
lens_1.query:
q = load "Master_Hierarchy";
q = filter q by 'Level_1' in  {{cell(Static_Region_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
q = filter q by {{column(lens_2.selection,["Region"]).asEquality('Level_1')}};
q = group q by ('Level_1', 'Level_2');

q = foreach q generate 
case when ('Level_1' == "AMER" && ('Level_2' ==  "Canada" )) then "Canada" 
when ('Level_1' == "AMER" && ('Level_2' ==  "United States" )) then "United States" 
when ('Level_1' == "AMER")then "RO AMER" 
when ('Level_1' == "EMEA" && ('Level_2' ==  "United Kingdom" )) then "United Kingdom"  
when ('Level_1' == "EMEA" && ('Level_2' ==  "France" )) then "France" 
when ('Level_1' == "EMEA" && ('Level_2' ==  "Germany" )) then "Germany" 
when ('Level_1' == "EMEA" && ('Level_2' ==  "Netherlands" )) then "Netherlands" 
when ('Level_1' == "EMEA" ) then "RO EMEA" 
when ('Level_1' == "APAC" && ('Level_2' ==  "Australia" )) then "ANZ"  
when ('Level_1' == "APAC" && ('Level_2' ==  "ANZ" )) then "ANZ"  
when ('Level_1' == "APAC" && ('Level_2' ==  "India" )) then "India" 
when ('Level_1' == "APAC" ) then "RO APAC" 
when ('Level_1' == "APAC" ) then "RO APAC"  
when ('Level_1' == "JP" && ('Level_2' == "Japan" )) then "Japan"
when ('Level_1' == "JP" && ('Level_2' == "South Korea")) then "South Korea"
when ('Level_1' == "JP") then "RO JP"  
when ('Level_1' == "LACA" && ('Level_2' ==  "Brazil" )) then "Brazil" 
when ('Level_1' == "LACA" ) then "RO LACA" 
when ('Level_1' == "Other" ) then "Other" else "ERROR" end as 'Country';

q = group q by 'Country'; 
q = foreach q generate 'Country'; 
q = order q by ('Country' asc);

parameters.text:
** DATA WILL BE UPDATED AS A PART OF THE REGULAR REFRESH BY MID AUGUST **
"Core Premier (A la Carte) & Priority" & "Signature" are included in  " Total" 
Customer = regional parent company excluding non-profit and zero-AOV customers
Addressable Market = Market size defined by Gartner/SFDC and does not sum across sub-products. Marketshare = AOV / Total Addressable Market.
Red Accounts: Account escalations that represent attriton risk (AOV)

** DATA (T&P Cost to Serve, Availability% and Transactions/requests) WILL BE UPDATED AS A PART OF THE REGULAR REFRESH BY MID AUGUST **
"Core Premier (A la Carte) & Priority" & "Signature" are included in  " Total"
SWE = Software Engineering IC's. Excludes SWE's Product Trust and Infra that are not working on product.
Infra: Represents total HC in the infrastructure organization
T&P Cost to Serve: Includes Infra, 3rd party royalty, and R&D + Products. Metric has 1 quarter lag (Q4 numbers are indicative of Q3 ending)
Availability %: Reflects core data centers onlyCPM total reflects core data centers only. Availability for sub-products may reflect total core data centers as well.

"Core Premier (A la Carte) & Priority" & "Signature" are included in  " Total" 
ACV: Availability of information in org62 can effect historical trends.
AOV: Availability of information in org62 can effect historical trends
Attrition: Trailing 12 months (TTM) attrition. Core only prior to FY15Q1. FY18 total attrition reflects SFDC excluding CC, Krux, and Heroku online business
** ATTRITION DATA AS OF MARCH FY19
Pipeline: Pipe numbers exclude CSG pipePipe Gen = Sum of $ amount of opportunities that moved to Stage 2. Note: Core pipe gen includes Premiere a-la-carte. The rest of CSG pipe gen is reported within CSG cut.

"Core Premier (A la Carte) & Priority" & "Signature" are included in  " Total" 
Within the AE, Co Prime, SE sections, % columns 3 & 4 represent 24 month CAGR (quarterly and YTD)
AEs: Includes ECS, Marketing Cloud (Messaging/Journies), and Commerce Cloud AE's
SEs: Excludes Q Branch, Spark, IPD, and SE Management
Co Prime: CSG Coprime = APs (account partners) that worked through the Qtr
